name: OrlandoFoodie
0:
”Alexa, what's my Flash Briefing?”
”Alexa, play my Flash Briefing”
skdetail:
Flash Briefing Skill
Rated: Mature. This skill contains: dynamic content.
des:
Orlando Foodie is an aggregator of news feeds from multiple critics, publications and blogs in the Orlando area to always know where the new brunch / lunch spot is.

Ever wonder what kinds of cool and trendy foods are in your area? Well my fellow foodies, now Orlando has an app just for that! Just ask Alexa and 
within seconds you'll know where and what good eats are near you!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
